  "original_title": "\u201c\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0ba8\u0bc0 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u201d : \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\u201cKota ne papa\u201d : Mano",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "There has been an agreement between opposition parties, Kalimuga militants and civil society to move towards the Presidential Secretariat in Colombo on Saturday 9th, encircle, and engage in peaceful anti-government demonstrations that took to the streets in their towns across the country.",
        "Tamil Progressive Alliance leader Mano Ganesan, who participated in the meeting on behalf of the opposition parties, told the media that",
        "The Tamil Progressive Alliance will fully participate in the full blockade to be held on Saturday 9th. Accordingly, on behalf of the Tamil Progressive Alliance, we request the hill plantation workers and plantation residents not to engage in work in the hill plantations on that day, but to participate in peaceful anti-government demonstrations.",
        "Similarly, on behalf of the Tamil Progressive Alliance, we are requesting all parties to close down the commercial establishments and offices in cities including Colombo and engage in anti-government demonstrations completely and allow their workplace workers to participate in the anti-government movement."
      ],
